<i>noun</i>: 희희낙락 [히히낭낙], 반색 [반색] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>희희낙락 [히히낭낙]</dt><br>
<dd>rejoicing; jubilation</dd><br>
<dd>매우 기뻐하고 즐거워함.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of being extremely happy and delighted.</dd><br>
<dt>반색 [반색]</dt><br>
<dd>rejoicing; being pleased</dd><br>
<dd>매우 반가운 마음을 얼굴에 드러냄.</dd><br>
<dd>A state of showing great joy on one's face.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>